<i>adverb</i>: 철저히 [철쩌히], 철두철미 [철뚜철미], 완전히 [완전히], 온전히 [온ː전히], 십상 [십쌍], 빈틈없이 [빈ː트멉씨], 꼭 [꼭], 고이 [고ː이], 감쪽같이 [감쪽까치] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>철저히 [철쩌히]</dt><br>
<dd>perfectly; immaculately; thoroughly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 하는 데 있어서 매우 조심하여 부족함이 없이 완벽하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being complete without flaws because one is very careful about something.</dd><br>
<dt>철두철미 [철뚜철미]</dt><br>
<dd>perfectly; immaculately; impeccably</dd><br>
<dd>처음부터 끝까지 빈틈이나 부족함이 없게.</dd><br>
<dd>Completely without flaws or defects.</dd><br>
<dt>완전히 [완전히]</dt><br>
<dd>completely; perfectly</dd><br>
<dd>부족한 점이 없이 모든 것이 갖추어져 모자람이나 흠이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of everything being provided without anything left out.</dd><br>
<dt>온전히 [온ː전히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. soundly; wholly</dd><br>
<dd>본래의 모습 그대로 고스란히.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of something being intact as it originally was.</dd><br>
<dd>2. perfectly; absolutely</dd><br>
<dd>잘못된 것이 없이 완벽하거나 올바르게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a perfect or accurate manner without any flaw.</dd><br>
<dt>십상 [십쌍]</dt><br>
<dd>fairly; perfectly</dd><br>
<dd>꼭 알맞게.</dd><br>
<dd>In an exactly adequate manner.</dd><br>
<dt>빈틈없이 [빈ː트멉씨]</dt><br>
<dd>1. without a missing part</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것이 빠져 있거나 어떤 부분이 비어 있지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>Without missing something or without having a vacant part.</dd><br>
<dd>2. perfectly</dd><br>
<dd>부족하거나 허술한 점이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without an incomplete or weak point.</dd><br>
<dt>꼭 [꼭]</dt><br>
<dd>1. without fail; at any cost; certainly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이 있어도 반드시.</dd><br>
<dd>By all means under any circumstances.</dd><br>
<dd>2. precisely</dd><br>
<dd>조금도 다르지 않고 정확하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Exactly without any difference.</dd><br>
<dd>3. perfectly</dd><br>
<dd>아주 잘.</dd><br>
<dd>Very well.</dd><br>
<dd>4. satisfactorily</dd><br>
<dd>매우 만족스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very satisfactory manner.</dd><br>
<dd>5. as if; just like</dd><br>
<dd>매우 비슷하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very similar way.</dd><br>
<dt>고이 [고ː이]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lovely; nicely</dd><br>
<dd>겉모습이 예쁘고 아름답게.</dd><br>
<dd>Prettily and beautifully in terms of one's outward appearance.</dd><br>
<dd>2. carefully</dd><br>
<dd>정성을 다하여 소중하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Gently with care.</dd><br>
<dd>3. in peace</dd><br>
<dd>편안하고 평화롭게.</dd><br>
<dd>Comfortably and peacefully.</dd><br>
<dd>4. perfectly; with nothing damaged</dd><br>
<dd>상태를 그대로 고스란히.</dd><br>
<dd>Just as it is.</dd><br>
<dt>감쪽같이 [감쪽까치]</dt><br>
<dd>seamlessly; perfectly</dd><br>
<dd>남이 알 수 없을 정도로 꾸미거나 고친 흔적이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without leaving any trace of decorating or mending that can be noticed.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>